snippet.title: Slasher's Keep - Full Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Slasher's Keep is a first-person roguelike with a focus on melee combat and loot.
Store link: http://store.steampowered.com/app/598060/Slashers_Keep/
Official website: http://www.slasherskeep.info

Thank you to everybody who supported the project during its Early Access period!
